---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Contact | Jennifer Chong — Corporate Governance Consultant Singapore"
  description="Book a free 30-minute board assessment call with Jennifer Chong. Contact Singapore's corporate governance expert for board audits, SGX compliance, and female director recruitment."
>

<!-- ===== PAGE HERO ===== -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label" style="color:var(--gold-light);">Get in Touch</span>
    <h1>Let's Talk About Your Board</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Book a free 30-minute assessment call or send a message. I'll respond within one business day.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== CONTACT LAYOUT ===== -->
<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-layout">

      <!-- LEFT: INFO -->
      <div>
        <div class="contact-info-card">
          <h3>Contact Details</h3>
          <div class="contact-info-item">
            <span class="contact-info-icon">📧</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Email</h4>
              <p><a href="mailto:jennifercly@gmail.com" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85); text-decoration:underline;">jennifercly@gmail.com</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-info-item">
            <span class="contact-info-icon">📞</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Phone / WhatsApp</h4>
              <p><a href="tel:+6585776630" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85); text-decoration:underline;">+65 8577 6630</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-info-item">
            <span class="contact-info-icon">📍</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Location</h4>
              <p>Singapore (clients across Southeast Asia)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-info-item">
            <span class="contact-info-icon">⏱</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Response Time</h4>
              <p>Within 1 business day</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="assessment-card">
          <h3>What Happens on a Free Assessment Call?</h3>
          <p>The free 30-minute call is a no-obligation conversation where I:</p>
          <ul class="check-list" style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <li>Listen to your board's specific challenges and goals</li>
            <li>Share an initial view on your governance position</li>
            <li>Recommend the most appropriate service or starting point</li>
            <li>Answer any questions about the process and investment</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--text-light); margin:0;">No hard sell. No obligation. Just a useful conversation about your board.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:1.5rem; padding:1.5rem 2rem; background:var(--gray-50); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); border:1px solid var(--gray-200);">
          <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:1rem;">Typical Enquiries</h4>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Board governance audit and SGX compliance review</li>
            <li>Female director recruitment and board diversity strategy</li>
            <li>Board effectiveness assessment</li>
            <li>Governance training for boards and committees</li>
            <li>Academic collaboration and speaking engagements</li>
            <li>PLS-SEM and quantitative research workshops</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: FORM -->
      <div class="contact-form">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.625rem;">Send a Message</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:2rem; color:var(--text-secondary); font-size:0.9375rem;">Fill in the form below and I'll be in touch within one business day.</p>

        <form novalidate>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="form-row">
              <div>
                <label for="first-name">First Name *</label>
                <input type="text" id="first-name" name="first_name" placeholder="e.g. Wei Ming" required>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="last-name">Last Name *</label>
                <input type="text" id="last-name" name="last_name" placeholder="e.g. Tan" required>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@company.com" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">Phone / WhatsApp</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="+65 XXXX XXXX">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="company">Company / Organisation</label>
            <input type="text" id="company" name="company" placeholder="Company name">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="role">Your Role</label>
            <select id="role" name="role">
              <option value="" disabled selected>Select your role</option>
              <option>Board Chair</option>
              <option>CEO / Managing Director</option>
              <option>Board Director</option>
              <option>Company Secretary</option>
              <option>CFO / Finance Director</option>
              <option>HR Director</option>
              <option>Academic / Researcher</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="service">Service of Interest</label>
            <select id="service" name="service">
              <option value="" disabled selected>What can I help you with?</option>
              <option>Free 30-Minute Assessment Call</option>
              <option>Board Governance Audit (Tier 1)</option>
              <option>Board Effectiveness Assessment (Tier 1)</option>
              <option>SGX Compliance Review (Tier 1)</option>
              <option>Audit + Strategy Package (Tier 2)</option>
              <option>Full Governance Transformation (Tier 3)</option>
              <option>Female Director Recruitment</option>
              <option>Governance Training Workshop</option>
              <option>PLS-SEM / Research Training</option>
              <option>Monthly Advisory Retainer</option>
              <option>Speaking / Academic Collaboration</option>
              <option>Other / Not Sure Yet</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Message *</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Tell me about your board's situation and what you're looking to achieve..." required></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="how-heard">How did you hear about me?</label>
            <select id="how-heard" name="how_heard">
              <option value="" disabled selected>Select an option</option>
              <option>LinkedIn</option>
              <option>Google Search</option>
              <option>Referral from a colleague</option>
              <option>Academic / conference network</option>
              <option>ERC Institute</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" style="width:100%; justify-content:center;">
            Send Message
          </button>

          <p style="font-size:0.8125rem; color:var(--text-light); text-align:center; margin-top:1rem; margin-bottom:0;">
            Your information is kept confidential and will never be shared with third parties.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== FAQ ===== -->
<section class="bg-gray">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">Common Questions</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-2">

      <div style="background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:1.75rem 2rem; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);" class="fade-up">
        <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">How long does a board governance audit take?</h4>
        <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.9375rem;">A standard Board Governance Audit typically takes 4–6 weeks from kick-off to final board presentation. This includes discovery, interviews, analysis, report writing, and presentation. Expedited timelines are possible for specific compliance needs.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:1.75rem 2rem; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);" class="fade-up">
        <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Do you work with non-SGX-listed companies?</h4>
        <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.9375rem;">Yes. While much of my expertise is SGX-specific, the governance frameworks and effectiveness principles apply to all boards — including private companies, family businesses, non-profits, and educational institutions.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:1.75rem 2rem; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);" class="fade-up">
        <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">How do you find female director candidates?</h4>
        <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.9375rem;">I draw on my professional networks, academic connections, and deep knowledge of Singapore's female director community. I identify candidates matched to your board's specific needs — sector, skills gaps, independence requirements — not generic profiles.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:1.75rem 2rem; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);" class="fade-up">
        <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Are engagements confidential?</h4>
        <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.9375rem;">Completely. All engagements are covered by a mutual confidentiality agreement. I never disclose client identities or findings. All board member interview responses are anonymised in reports.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:1.75rem 2rem; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);" class="fade-up">
        <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Can I start with a smaller engagement before committing to a full audit?</h4>
        <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.9375rem;">Absolutely. Many clients start with an SGX Compliance Review or Board Composition Review before engaging in a full governance audit. The free 30-minute assessment call is the ideal first step to determine the right scope.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:1.75rem 2rem; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);" class="fade-up">
        <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Do you offer payment plans or phased billing?</h4>
        <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.9375rem;">Yes. For longer engagements, fees can be structured in milestone-based payments aligned to deliverable stages. Discuss your preferred arrangement during our initial call and I'll accommodate where possible.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
